终生上门服务，售后第一时间响应</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:52px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 19px\">③&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">原料保障：</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">出口级高纯优质尿素原料，全国物流配送中心</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 19px\">三大优势</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:67px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px\">（1）&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">小型</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">·</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">简单：</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">一体</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">机，仅需</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">3m</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;vertical-align:super\">2</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">；</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">一键操作</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">，工作从来如此简单。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:67px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px\">（2）&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">短链供应</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">：</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">切断分销渠道，</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">成本降低</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">60%</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">，让</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">您的</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">利润最大化。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:67px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-weight:bold;font-size:19px\">（3）&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\">智能化：</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">手机、电脑远程实时管控</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">、</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">实时</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\">诊断。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:67px\"></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体;font-size: 21px\">品质管控</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:45px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">①&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">线上管控</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:23px;text-indent:43px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">新蓝智能生产系统，实时管控品质。传感器采集数据，上传云端，<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">网络传输到总部平台和客户手机客户端。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:45px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">②&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">线下检测</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:23px;text-indent:43px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">新蓝自有实验室，与多家高校合作，免费提供品质检验服务提供第三方权威技术检验。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><br/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px\">低成本投入</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"position:absolute;z-index:1;left:0px;margin-left:3.0000px;margin-top:14.0000px;width:18.0000px;height:20.0000px\"><img width=\"18\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://www.new-blue.cc/Public/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ADMINI~1\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wpsBF79.tmp.png\" style=\"background:url(http://www.new-blue.cc/Public/ueditor/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">提供3m</span><sup><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px;vertical-align:super\">2</span></sup><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">安装区</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"position:absolute;z-index:1;left:0px;margin-left:4.0000px;margin-top:13.4000px;width:18.0000px;height:20.0000px\"><img width=\"18\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://www.new-blue.cc/Public/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:\\Users\\ADMINI~1\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wpsBF8A.tmp.png\" style=\"background:url(http://www.new-blue.cc/Public/ueditor/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">水、电配套供应</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 21px\">行业前景</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:53px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">宏观因素。</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">我国整体宏观经济保持着强劲的增长姿势。据预计，我国经济今年增幅将在<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右，宏观经济的继续增长，推动我国重型卡车的销售量，车用尿素应用市场也随之增大。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:53px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">微观因素。</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">随着</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">国家</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">排放标准的陆续实施，</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">以及国五、国六标准越来越严格，</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">车用尿素</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">需求</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">量</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">必将</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">逐步增大。从柴油车保有量上来看，市场需求将实现快速增长。<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年国内重型柴油车销售</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">88.06</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆，</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年销售</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">63.6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆，</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年全年销售</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">75</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">~76</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆。相关专业人士预测，其中配备</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">SCR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统的重型柴油车将至少以每年</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆的速度增长，</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年底理论上可达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">225</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万辆。按照柴油车产量测算，预计到</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2018</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年我国车用尿素市场容量将达</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">700</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万吨</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:21px\">，按照市场价格<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">吨计算，未来市场份额将达到</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">140</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">亿</span></span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:21px\">。因此，车用尿素市场规模急剧增加将成为大势所趋</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size: 21px\">。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:67px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px\"><br/></span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><br/></strong><br/></p>','0','','1467216000','1467852706','0','0','1','500','','','','','','/Uploads/2016_07_07/577da6e500ab7.jpg','','');
